                "caption": "Figure 1:Overview of RoboDojo.RoboDojo unifies efficient simulation evaluation and reproducible real-world testing for generalist robot manipulation, covering 42 simulation tasks, 18 real-world tasks, heterogeneous parallel simulation, RoboDojo-RealEval, XPolicyLab, and a continuously updated leaderboard.",
